               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380709-name-427" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-427" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-427" type="surname" value="ROPER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-427" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES ROPER</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a shop in Charlotte-street, Whitechapel. The prisoner came there on the 7th of July three or four times—he looked a some things, but did not buy any—on the following morning I missed this drill and cloth (<hi rend="italic">looking at them</hi>) which had been safe in my window at four o'clock the day before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
