                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-428" type="surname" value="REARDON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-428" type="given" value="JOHN JOSEPH"></interp>JOHN JOSEPH REARDON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Aaron, a pawnbrokes in Whitechapel-road. Last Saturday evening, between five and six o'clock, the prisoner came to pawn a piece of drill like that produced—I saw he was in liquor, and I would not take it in.</p>
               <p>
