                  </hi>. I am the wife of Samuel Minton, and keep a woollen<lb></lb>draper's shop, in Duke-street, Aldgate. On Saturday, the 7th of July, the prisoner brought this piece of drill and this bit of cloth to me—I bought the cloth for 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I did not buy the drill.</p>
